An advanced, visually appealing chatbot that:
- Greets the user
- Lets the user select a role (Student, Researcher, Analyst)
- Accepts input via text, voice, and file upload
- Connects to GPT-3.5-turbo (via OpenRouter API)
- Reads out the bot's responses (speech output)
- Shows a live analytics dashboard (messages sent, files uploaded)
- Supports Dark Mode toggle ğŸŒ‘
- Uploads and saves files locally
- Beautiful, animated UI âœ¨

